data.description: The Hawthorne plan is our most spacious one-story home in the gorgeous community of Morningside Trails. This home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and an attached two-car garage. The Hawthorne boasts a large, open concept family room, perfect for entertaining family and friends. This home comes with thousands of dollars in upgrades included, such as granite countertops, energy-efficient appliances, a WiFi-enabled garage door opener, USB outlets in the kitchen, and more.
